children.strValue: The Perfect Winter Cap from Novara
These three hats combined into one from Novara
Like a reduction in cooking, the new winter cycling cap from REI thickens and intensifies the ingredients from three hats into one.

, old-school ear flaps from one made of merino wool, and thin, warm Italian fabric. I’d like to think Bike Hugger had some influence on this hat; ensuring it fits under a helmet, isn’t too hot, and will survive repeated wash and dry cycles.
